{"id":110715,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2010/10/简讯：中国将购买希腊国债/","date":"2010-10-03T17:34:07Z","modified":"2010-10-03T17:34:07Z","title":"简讯：中国将购买希腊国债","content":"<div>\n<p>正在访问雅典的中国总理温家宝表示，一旦希腊回到国际市场后，将购买希腊的国债。</p>\n<p>评论指出，这显示了中国政府对饱受经济困扰的希腊的支持。</p>\n<p>中国官方在温家宝出访欧洲前表示，中国将采取实际行动支持希腊、欧元和欧盟尽快摆脱危机并获得稳步复苏。</p>\n</p></div>\n<div>\n</div>\n<p><a href=\"http://feedads.g.doubleclick.net/~a/2-G4jFSpOi7TkO_Txx3tzfcERCY/0/da\"><img border=\"0\" ismap src=\"http://feedads.g.doubleclick.net/~a/2-G4jFSpOi7TkO_Txx3tzfcERCY/0/di\"></a><br />\n<a href=\"http://feedads.g.doubleclick.net/~a/2-G4jFSpOi7TkO_Txx3tzfcERCY/1/da\"><img border=\"0\" ismap src=\"http://feedads.g.doubleclick.net/~a/2-G4jFSpOi7TkO_Txx3tzfcERCY/1/di\"></a></p>\n<div>\n<a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?a=7Db3fN8vIbc:JNYOqV-uzDo:mqyYa2mfVbY\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?d=mqyYa2mfVbY\" /></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?a=7Db3fN8vIbc:JNYOqV-uzDo:PFx2F_oWK34\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?d=PFx2F_oWK34\" /></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?a=7Db3fN8vIbc:JNYOqV-uzDo:DUWcskeyX7o\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?d=DUWcskeyX7o\" /></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?a=7Db3fN8vIbc:JNYOqV-uzDo:clraHZBW0_I\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?d=clraHZBW0_I\" /></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?a=7Db3fN8vIbc:JNYOqV-uzDo:qj6IDK7rITs\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?d=qj6IDK7rITs\" /></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?a=7Db3fN8vIbc:JNYOqV-uzDo:7Q72WNTAKBA\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?d=7Q72WNTAKBA\" /></a>\n</div>\n<p><img height=\"1\" src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/cnbbc/~4/7Db3fN8vIbc\" width=\"1\" /></p>\n<p>请看原文：<br />\n<a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.bbc.co.uk/zhongwen/simp/business/2010/10/10100